Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好困
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.86,0:00:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.70,0:00:17.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来你裙子的口袋里放着纸巾就那样放进洗衣篮了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.58,0:00:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是够呛的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:20.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:24.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有以后先把要洗的衣物好好分类哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.75,0:00:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是我家的篮子…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.92,0:00:28.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.21,0:00:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别那么斤斤计较你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.42,0:00:32.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是男人的话  就应该堂堂…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.09,0:00:35.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来一发猛的吧  耶耶耶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.72,0:00:39.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来一发猛的吧  耶耶耶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.51,0:00:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  耶  来吧  耶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.35,0:00:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来一发猛的吧  耶耶耶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.78,0:00:52.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别介意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.70,0:00:54.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:00:59.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个该我出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长加油
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.91,0:01:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢声援  诸位
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栉枝…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.42,0:01:12.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  放马过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.84,0:01:15.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那清爽的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.68,0:01:22.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.35,0:01:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栉枝  那闪闪发光的汗水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.69,0:01:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一垒  耶  二垒  耶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.44,0:01:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绕过三垒本垒打
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.74,0:01:40.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那精神过头的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:46.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上本垒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.08,0:01:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  栉枝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.71,0:01:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今早也…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.68,0:01:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,视线太色了  你这恶心狗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:00.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栉枝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.89,0:02:03.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于周末的男女混合练习的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.22,0:02:06.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  北村同学我也正好…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:08.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  还不懂吗笨狗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.44,0:02:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  停手…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.61,0:02:12.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}喂  给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:15.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连回家部今天早上也是精神饱满呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:19.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,健康第一嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:04:00.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装饰手机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小实手指真灵巧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.88,0:04:04.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿  还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看我这样  手指可是很灵巧的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栉枝  在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.73,0:04:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  一机完成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:21.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  接着是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛发出被勒死一样的声音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.29,0:04:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也给高须同学的做一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:04:37.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在装饰手机店里打工呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:38.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,专…专业人士？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用紫色的小珠子给你嵌上「龙儿」的图案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:45.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}手机上：龙儿  LOVE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栉枝她…为了我？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:51.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栉枝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.06,0:04:54.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的也拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:56.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  来订单了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:03.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那在这张单子上写上名字还有想要的颜色和图案
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:05.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  我的是粉红色…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.36,0:05:06.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大大的心型
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.91,0:05:07.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:08.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常可爱的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.66,0:05:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样也很可爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为打工做了手机装饰的专业人士了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪闪发光的栉枝和闪闪发光的装饰手机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可思议般地合适啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  泰泰今晚要出去陪酒不在家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么菜我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:31.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还说「龙儿」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.35,0:05:34.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连后面的名字也记住了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:37.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为我一直这样叫的缘故吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.06,0:05:40.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起那个泰泰的那份菜…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.48,0:05:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  和她说了好多话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.53,0:05:46.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说大河  我说话的时候有没有紧…张？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我好好听人说话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便告诉你  紧张得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.33,0:05:59.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  晚饭还没做好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:06:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:01.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是  就快好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是盖浇饭  吃完了就赶紧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:06.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电饭锅…坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临  晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:20.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,点～什么～好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还专程来家庭餐厅…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然没饭吃  还有面包啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁着现在就吠吧  劣等狗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:31.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快你就会跪着感谢我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:35.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来咯  这是您点的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:38.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还什么都没点…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.58,0:06:40.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:46.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然要保密  这可是冰淇淋大增量的大河特别版哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.42,0:06:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃的时候可别让其他客人看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:50.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以来谢谢了  小实
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.55,0:06:53.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以来？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:56.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高须同学不喜欢吃甜的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.47,0:06:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要换成炸薯条吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:02.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大份哦  超大份哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.23,0:07:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不  我是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:09.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小实在便利店和卡拉OK厅也有打工呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  上周开始还加上火锅店
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么多？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:16.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样已经节制了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何作为女子垒球部的部长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:21.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社团活动可是不能休息的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.25,0:07:25.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么拼命工作  难道有什么想要的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.75,0:07:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有时间啊  不勤劳怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勤劳？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  「勤劳怪奇档案」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}注：日语发音接近日本电视连续剧「银狼怪奇档案」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苏醒的勤劳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.26,0:07:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来  关系真好呢你们两位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:46.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐  来点冷水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:08.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天一天里我的视力明显地下降了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:12.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劣等狗一只  还看着小实的餐厅制服流口水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.34,0:08:15.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「她的笑容闪闪发光啊」这样想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛…别再戳眼睛了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:27.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再戳会弄脏我的手指
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:34.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  为什么会打这么多的工呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:37.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说了是「勤劳怪奇档案」了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:44.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说有什么需要钱的理由吗  家里的事什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:46.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了救生病的母亲什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说了「勤劳」了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.59,0:08:56.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种想法还是抛弃比较好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:09:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「只有我才能理解真正的她」这种想法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:03.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恶心得我想吐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:08.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离我远一点走  你太恶心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:12.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  大河
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:14.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊这种说话方式  太冷淡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:16.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了别靠过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:20.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我有对你不冷淡过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨  小鹦久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:28.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的晚饭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:33.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大份哦  超大份哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹦鹉  鹦鹉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:38.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要来吗  小鹦  要说出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:39.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹦鹉  鹦鹉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:41.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,演歌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:10:00.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀  休息日的早晨真是很清爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.20,0:09:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}去吃早饭了  冰箱里有三明治  小龙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧  大河
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是不该告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:07.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:11.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃做饭  为了去见小实而去家庭餐厅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电饭锅还是坏的也没办法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.51,0:10:17.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样应该先去电器店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:20.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你不是说了不喜欢吃面包
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上的话也可以  就算是面包
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊这么得意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那衣服不适合你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像忘东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:32.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不远就让我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正穿什么都不会变的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:36.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？  小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是魅罗乃的儿子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稻毛家的大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.41,0:10:44.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魅罗乃？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:47.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  是泰子的花名
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:49.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作地方的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.09,0:10:57.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出了剪票口  一直往前走200米
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.51,0:11:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是昆沙门天国的魅罗乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来几岁？23？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猜对了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天一大早运气真好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:13.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魅罗乃的DNA  Touch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好呢真好呢  有点紧绷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.11,0:11:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年轻真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:19.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么觉得这个大叔真让人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:25.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢着两位
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没吃早饭的话  推荐这个不饱和脂肪酸富含钙的鱼肉烧哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栉枝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小实？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  把这个搬去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:46.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.23,0:11:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是我来搬吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:11:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魅罗乃的儿子还是安心地去喝茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.61,0:12:02.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我一定要做…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的事啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.53,0:12:08.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然只限休息日  我正在找打工的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栉枝  要好好干活哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:12.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦～交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.08,0:12:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近很忙啊  人手不足
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人手？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:21.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.67,0:12:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和栉枝是朋友的话  你要不要也来试试打工
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会加工钱的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.51,0:12:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.35,0:12:36.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和这家伙一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.82,0:12:45.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  别惹事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:50.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会给栉枝添麻烦的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你一个人来帮忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:12:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小不点  送货拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:57.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的啤酒三箱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:00.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  非常乐意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  这样就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.59,0:13:08.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  大河？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:23.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该不会是不会骑自行车…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:29.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.91,0:13:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会骑自行车又怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我搬过去就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弄错了  弄错了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,激情四射呀  大河
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.17,0:13:43.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真勇猛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  推着去的话很安全…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  对了  要补充点烧酒来着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.39,0:13:56.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:13:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  什么都不做的话还是会过意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.65,0:14:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就拜托你咯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.88,0:14:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  芋头烧酒在…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:31.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太暗了看不清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  因为这里很少使用的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:37.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多也就是一周打开一次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.56,0:14:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被关在里面的话那就不得了了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.81,0:14:44.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会让人有遇难了的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:51.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个小不点就这样把门开着  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:14:59.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  里面还有人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:02.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,SOS  SOS
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要冷静  高须同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:07.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栉枝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是在这种时候才会有效果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:13.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,效果？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:39.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真像个傻子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全没有这么努力的必要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:46.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是干不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:47.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么干不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北…北村同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:57.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为…为什么  在…这这这…里？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:15:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在自我锻炼中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  这是逢坂的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  嘛  差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能骑自行车了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不得了的进步呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.45,0:16:20.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  与其说能骑…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你会知道我不会骑自行车
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为去年我很仔细地观察过你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:37.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自行车真好啊  世界会变得宽广
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么逢坂  明天见了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:52.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去年  观察我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.54,0:17:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.54,0:17:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有北村同学看着我的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算宽广也没意义啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.39,0:17:26.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:30.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二三…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.49,0:17:35.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢  怎么这么慢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:36.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个样子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:39.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么  比起那个另外两个人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:44.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来  栉枝那家伙去哪儿闲逛了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:46.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙儿就算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.67,0:17:52.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在努力的时候  那只劣等狗居然在优雅地偷着懒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.84,0:17:54.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:56.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起那个  这次是三号街的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:18:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙儿  你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.31,0:18:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～啊～通往未来的桥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:14.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是桥  桥…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:17.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗓子都干了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么大声居然也没人注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这个时间大叔专注于赛马
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:28.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微有点冷了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:29.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不介意的话  我的衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  暖和一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.09,0:18:38.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,投手在害怕着  嘿嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:42.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,投手在害怕着  嘿嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.51,0:18:44.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正害怕着…  投手不是栉枝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕着  嘿  害怕着  嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,投手正害怕着  嘿嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,投手正害怕着  嘿嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.73,0:18:52.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕着  哈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.98,0:18:55.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的害怕了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.74,0:18:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为手在颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:02.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真讨厌  这是因为兴奋啊  因为兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.82,0:19:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看好  要去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.79,0:19:13.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了换人  攻守交换
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:15.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:18.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.22,0:19:20.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕也没用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:22.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:26.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要把怯懦打飞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.93,0:19:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栉枝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.27,0:19:31.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.94,0:19:35.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  高须同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:38.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是能从那里出去？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.15,0:19:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里  在哪里  在哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:48.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在  哪  里～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  高须同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:19:59.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定  栉枝看上去总是那么耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.88,0:20:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不只是因为她开朗有活力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.43,0:20:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危…危险
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.64,0:20:11.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栉枝  抱歉  没事吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:13.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  鼻  鼻血
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:17.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:18.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.15,0:20:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鼻血是心灵的汗水哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:23.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  比起这个还差一点了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:25.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堆吧  堆上去高须
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:26.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.33,0:20:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把怯懦打飞…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.25,0:20:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  一定要生还哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.54,0:20:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  当然了  Fight！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.96,0:20:41.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  说到Fight的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:43.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一  一发？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:45.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.26,0:20:46.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.39,0:20:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一  一发
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.51,0:20:50.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栉枝从一开始就那么闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:20:56.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相遇的时候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:20:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.69,0:20:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一发
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪耀着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.78,0:21:13.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找  到  你  了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.59,0:21:28.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大河  你怎么来这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:32.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么来…  用梯子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.35,0:21:35.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  高须同学这样就能出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.14,0:21:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.69,0:21:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你了  大河
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:40.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样才是通往未来的梯子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:41.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个啊  小实
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.44,0:21:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  高须同学也快点起来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.32,0:21:44.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.36,0:21:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不是说了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.82,0:21:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梯子刚才掉下去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.34,0:23:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在心里悄悄藏起的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.63,0:23:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能对任何人说的只属于两个人的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.80,0:23:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经和高须说过了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.26,0:23:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北北  北村…
